Step1 - https://github.com/damianszczepanik/maven-cucumber-reporting

damianszczepanik


Step 2 - Use the pom from this project

Step 3 -  Add version as per version number provided on https://github.com/damianszczepanik/maven-cucumber-reporting
in the plugin 
<plugin>
                <groupId>net.masterthought</groupId>
                <artifactId>maven-cucumber-reporting</artifactId>
                <version>5.7.0</version>
                
                
Steo 3 - In the runner add 

plugin = "json:target/jsonReports/cucumber-report.json"

Step 4 : In the terminal run , mvn test verify

ensure you are connected to vpn for maven dependencies download

